<h3>Connected to text_controller.js</h3>
<h4>Controller will warn user when they are close to or over the maximum character count (set to 90% of max)</h4>
<h4>The controller was built to work with varying character limits, set using data attributes</h4>
<div data-controller="text"
     data-text-char-limit-value=10>
  <p>Example (char limit: 10):</p>
  <p class="warning" data-text-target="warning"></p>
  <textarea data-text-target="textArea" data-action="text#checkLimit"></textarea>
</div>
<div data-controller="text"
     data-text-char-limit-value=20>
  <p>Example (char limit: 20):</p>
  <p class="warning" data-text-target="warning"></p>
  <textarea data-text-target="textArea" data-action="text#checkLimit"></textarea>
</div>
